title: NOW Foods Rose Hip Seed Oil, 1 ounce
description: Rich in Omega-6 essential fatty acids, Rose Hip Seed Oil continues to serve as one of the personal care industry's most sought-after natural oils.  NOW® Rose Hip Seed Oil is 100% Pure and Natural, and extracted from the seeds of Rose mosqueta.

title: Margot Elena Tokyo Milk's Kabuki, 1 Fluid Ounce
description: Differentiate yourself with this complex blend of notes. Featured in o, allure, and in style magazine. A decidedly different collection of brilliantly paired fragrance notes housed in an alluring glass bottle decorated with an iconic image of Japanese theater.

title: Clairol Perfect 10 by Nice 'n Easy Hair Color, 007.5A, Medium Ash Blonde
description: Perfect 10 provides high gloss hair color in just 10 minutes. It has an advanced color crème with micro-pearls that gently accelerates the color development process, delivering rich, high gloss color and 100% gray coverage in just 10 minutes, while better protecting your hair*.
